This is a test&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>About</title><link>https://kachanimbu.com/about/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://kachanimbu.com/about/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;I am Vimal. This is my space to share thoughts and ideas on anything that crosses my mind.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I got tired of using AI for everything — even personal messages — and I had begun losing the knack to write properly. This is my attempt to keep that part alive in me.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an outlet full of contradictions, weirdness, and mistakes. But this is me. Anything I write won&amp;rsquo;t be perfect, won&amp;rsquo;t be great — it&amp;rsquo;ll be average. And average is awesome.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>